values: So where shall i begin... i dunno how to start this but basically i'm feeling down :-( Yesterday was such a blast but on the way home from the sports centre with Jay it was raining and i went down a hill turned a corner fell off and slid along the road - friction burn ouchh! today... well i dunno it's just nothing seems right... its wierd i'm just stuck in this horrible mood where all i can do is think about things and wish they were better - stupid hey but u guys just can;t understand what i feel atm. sorry to write about such shit guys i wish i had something happy to say but i can;t think of nything right now! i need a hug! luv ya all!!

oh yeah!!! it's true i can officially surf, well plzed! i stood for the first time... for lyk 2seconds... but still i stood! Finished schl for half-term should b a blast as Jamie is coming ova for the week ... wooo! i am lyk so siked!
